Rosina Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosina_Lawrence 0 Rosina May Lawrence (December 30, 1912 – June 23, 1997) was a British-Canadian actress and singer. She had a short but memorable career in the 1920s and 1930s in Hollywood before she married in 1939 and retired from entertainment.
